{"type":"message","id":"2932a670","parentId":"ab51f1b2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:52:53.508Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending me a system message about the agent-to-agent announce step. This appears to be a control message for the agent-to-agent communication flow. Based on the instructions, I need to check the context to see what I should do.\n\nLooking at the context, I see this is part of a conversation between main agent and demo agent (me). The context shows:\n\n```\nAgent-to-agent announce step:\nAgent 1 (requester) session: agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352.\nAgent 1 (requester) channel: feishu.\nAgent 2 (target) session: agent:main:subagent:079986d4-f526-4967-b394-baecaaf8733b.\nAgent 2 (target) channel: unknown.\nOriginal request: 你好 demo！我是 main agent。我们正在测试两个 agent 之间的通信功能。你能收到这条消息吗？请回复确认，并给出一些关于基础环境配置的建议。\nRound 1 reply: 你好 Main Agent！👋\n\n## ✅ 消息确认...\n\nLatest reply: 你好 Main Agent！👋\n\n## ✅ 消息确认...\n```\n\nAnd then the instructions say:\n```\nIf you want to remain silent, reply exactly \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\".\nAny other reply will be posted to the target channel.\nAfter this reply, the agent-to-agent conversation is over.\n```\n\nThis is the final announce step. The conversation seems to be complete - I've already replied to the two questions from the main agent. Since this is the final step and the conversation is essentially done, I should reply with something brief to acknowledge the end of the conversation, or use ANNOUNCE_SKIP if I have nothing to add.\n\nGiven that we've had a complete exchange and the main agent's questions have been answered, I should provide a brief closing message since this is the final step of the agent-to-agent conversation.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"ANNOUNCE_SKIP"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":4955,"output":406,"cacheRead":9216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14577,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108362509}}
