{"type":"message","id":"41896919","parentId":"ab2ce243","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:53:18.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了一个\"Agent-to-agent announce step\"消息，这看起来是一个系统级的agent间通信步骤。根据之前的上下文，我作为subagent已经完成了任务，并且在上一轮中已经回复了详细的技术建议。\n\n用户再次发送\"Agent-to-agent announce step\"，这可能是：\n1. 系统正在尝试完成agent-to-agent通信的结束步骤\n2. 测试是否还会收到回复\n\n根据系统提示：\"If you want to remain silent, reply exactly \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\". Any other reply will be posted to the target channel. After this reply, the agent-to-agent conversation is over.\"\n\n这意味着我应该回复\"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\"来保持沉默，因为：\n1. 我已经完成了所有实质性的技术回答\n2. 这是一个announce step，不需要额外内容\n3. 回复其他内容会被发送到目标频道，可能造成干扰\n\n所以我应该回复\"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\"。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"ANNOUNCE_SKIP"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":5383,"output":182,"cacheRead":9216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108392385}}
